title: Patricia Brooks
text: I have ordered many things from this company. ( Stickerkid ) Their workmanship is awesome..My grandkid's luv everything that was from Stickerkid...My grandkids are like Meme can we get more stickers & etc..They wear me out towards wanting new things from Stickerkid...All I can say...I trust this Company ( Stickerkid ) I hope they will always stay & be awesome....
